## Why this is a separate PR
The regression test (tests/trace/test_op_static_typing.py, added in PR1) shells out
to a type checker and self-skips when one is absent. Without mypy in the test deps it
SKIPS in CI (no gate). Adding mypy turns it into a real gate but touches pyproject +
uv.lock (a dependency decision with broader blast radius), so it is isolated here. PR1
can land alone if maintainers don't want the dep; the test still runs locally / wherever
mypy exists.

