  adding mypy, not uv-version drift.
- Pinning `<2` (mypy 1.20.2) still churned the same 92 3.14-marker lines (librt is pulled
  in on 1.x too).
- FIX: constrain to `python_version < '3.14'`. Tests run on 3.10-3.13 (3.12 primary); 3.14
  is not a target. Result: 0 removed, 151 added (just the mypy/librt/pathspec package
  blocks + hashes). No existing package versions change.

